picture_counter_0 A single, vibrant red maple leaf rests on a smooth, light-gray stone surface. The leaf is fully intact, with five pointed lobes and delicate veins clearly visible. Soft, natural daylight highlights its glossy surface and subtle color gradients from deep crimson at the edges to lighter scarlet near the stem. The background is softly out of focus, emphasizing the leaf’s crisp edges and rich texture.


## 科室简介

呼吸与危重症医学科为医院重点建设科室之一，拥有完善的诊疗体系与专业设备，长期承担区域医疗服务任 务。


